<div class="body-inv">
    <p>Welcome to our inventory page. At Wheelin' N Dealin', we are sure to have any vehicle that fits your needs. We
        have a wide variety of all types of vehicles from the best manufactors such as Chevy, Ford, Toyota and others.
    </p>
    <p>Find your next car, truck or SUV with Wheelin' N Dealin', our entire inventory is shown below!
    </p>
