        needs without browsing through our entire catalog.</p>
    <ul class="inv">
        <div>Wheelin' N Dealin' 2019 Inventory</div>
        <p>_________________________________________</p>
        {{#each cars}}
            {{#unless hidden}}
                Your favorite new car is a....<br>
                {{year}} {{make}} {{model}}<br>
                {{color}} {{type}}<br>
                Mileage: {{mileage}}<br>
                Asking Price: ${{price}}<br>
                <img src={{image}}><br>
